WEBVTT

00:00:01.875 --> 00:00:04.059
I am an architect.

00:00:04.083 --> 00:00:07.976
And this picture shows the city
that I come from,

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:09.934
Beijing, China.

00:00:09.958 --> 00:00:14.059
And old Beijing is like
a very beautiful garden,

00:00:14.083 --> 00:00:16.184
you can see a lot of nature.

00:00:16.208 --> 00:00:17.601
When I was a kid,

00:00:17.625 --> 00:00:19.934
I learned to swim in this lake

00:00:19.958 --> 00:00:23.184
and I climbed mountains
every day after school.

00:00:23.208 --> 00:00:25.101
But after getting older,

00:00:25.125 --> 00:00:28.476
we built more and more modern buildings.

00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:30.351
And they all look the same.